flowchart TD
    A[songs.csv] -->|load_songs| B[List of Song Dicts]
    C[User Preferences] --> D[recommend_songs]
    B --> D

    D --> E{Score Each Song}

    E --> F[Mood Match\nweight: 1.0]
    E --> G[Energy Closeness\nweight: 2.0]
    E --> H[Valence Closeness\nweight: 1.5]
    E --> I[Danceability Closeness\nweight: 1.5]
    E --> J[Acousticness Pref\nweight: 1.0]

    F --> K[Sum Scores\nmax: 7.0]
    G --> K
    H --> K
    I --> K
    J --> K

    K --> L[Sort by Score DESC]
    L --> M[Return Top K Songs\nwith Explanations]
    M --> N[Print Results]
